CRUD ACTIONS
------------

CREATE
> new     - display new record form
> create  - process new record form (submited from new)

READ
> index   - list records
> show    - display single record

UPDATE
> edit    - display edit record form
> update  - process edit record form

DELETE
> delete  - display delete record form
> destroy - process delete record form


CONTROLLERS:

1 ctrl per model
Plural names
